The updated preliminary plan submitted to the City can be reviewed by clicking on the thumbnail below. The initial site plan submitted in March 2016 envisioned a nearly 378,000 square foot IKEA store with surface parking, additional retail/restaurant spaces, and possibly a 75-room hotel. The revised conceptual site plan shows a proposed 339,000 square foot IKEA store with integrated podium parking and a 92,600 square foot commercial center with a mix of retail and restaurant spaces. This revised site plan is under review and is still being refined. An environmental analysis of the proposed project has begun.
